text.section:
A committee shall not, however:
Authorize or approve distributions, except according to a formula or method, or within limits, prescribed by the board of directors;
Approve or propose to shareholders action that this chapter requires be approved by shareholders;
Fill vacancies on the board of directors or, subject to the provisions of subsection (7) of this section, on any of its committees; or
Adopt, amend, or repeal bylaws.
